name: THEY ARE ALREADY DEAD ( but they have not been warned)
name_original: THEY ARE ALREADY DEAD ( but they have not been warned)
description:
PRESS ENTER TO START

Z TO NORMAL MODE, X TO EASY MODE

Kill all enemies before countdown ends!

(well, you can also play easy mode without countdown)

You can do wall jumps!

Press Esc in any moment to go back to the title.

Thanks for playing!
